==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Levanter
<hw>Le*vant"er</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From <er>Levant</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>A strong easterly wind peculiar to the
Mediterranean.</def> <rj><au>W. H. Russell.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Levantine</ent>⟦br⟧
